Set up the project structure and initial UI components for the fitness app

This commit initializes the project with a `.replit` configuration, a `.gitignore` file, and various UI components for the fitness tracking application. It includes setup for routing, navigation, and basic elements like buttons, cards, and forms, leveraging Radix UI and Tailwind CSS for a modern and responsive user interface.

